free:
https://www.adbeat.com/ -- give this tool any business and it'll spit out the publishers posting their ads and estimated impression counts for each. 
https://www.similarweb.com/ -- enter a website URL in the search bar, and you gain access to insights such as traffic sources, organic versus paid search, social traffic and related sites.
paid:
https://www.owletter.com/ -- a tool that lets you analyze marketing emails from any company 
